# SuccessPilot AI - System Architecture

## 1. Project Overview

SuccessPilot AI is a GenAI-powered Customer Success SaaS platform designed to help businesses improve customer onboarding, engagement, support automation, and customer retention.

The platform uses AI agents, automation workflows, and knowledge management to assist Customer Success teams.

